tool_description: We understand how important it is to spread joy and laughter, especially in today's world. That's why we created the ultimate Joke API, designed to be your partner in bringing humor to your audience. Our vast collection of jokes is easy to integrate and perfect for making your digital spaces more lively and engaging. Let's make the world a happier place, one joke at a time. Start now and see the difference it makes!
name: BestJokeAPI
title: BestJokeAPI

api_list.name: /jokes/produce
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://bestjokeapi.p.rapidapi.com/jokes/produce"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "bestjokeapi.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
